  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink31-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> muṉṉorunāḷ taṉṉōṭu putuppuṉalāṭuḻi, ‘iṉip puṟattoḻukkam virumpēṉ’ eṉa
          āyattārōṭu cūḷuṟṟa talaimakaṉ piṉpum parattaiyarōṭu puṉalāṭat toṭaṅkukiṉṟāṉ eṉpatu kēṭṭa
          talaimakaḷ avaṉuḻaiyar kēṭpat tōḻikkuc colliyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink31">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi makiḻnaṉ</l>
          <l> kaṭaṉaṉ ṟeṉṉuṅ kollō nammūr </l>
          <l> muṭamutir marutattup peruntuṟai</l>
          <l> yuṭaṉā ṭāyamō ṭuṟṟa cūḷē.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> Alas, [my] friend! </l>
          <l> They say that a man who delights cannot be virtuous, do they not?</l>
          <l> [Remember] the oath that was sworn, in front of [our] friends when we were bathing together</l>
          <l> at the big ghat in our village with its crooked, old myrobalan trees?</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
